<p>The rsync master will stay unavailable for now.</p>
<p>I've asked the hoster to look into the issue, but I can't currently estimate when I'll get a reply/fix.</p>
<p>Sorry for the inconvenience,
Florian</p>") (creator nil "Florian Pritz") (pubDate nil "Thu, 08 Oct 2015 08:10:48 +0000") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "tag:www.archlinux.org,2015-10-08:/news/downtime-rsync-mail/")))) ("ttf-dejavu 2.37 will require forced upgrade" "<p><a href=\"https://www.archlinux.org/packages/extra/any/ttf-dejavu/\">ttf-dejavu</a> 2.37 will change the way fontconfig configuration is installed. In previous versions the configuration was symlinked from post_install/post_upgrade, the new version will place the files inside the package like it is done in fontconfig now.</p>
